{"tid":298084,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜鍾舒漫","createTime":"2017-06-26T04:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T02:52:35.000Z","uid":124662,"like":39,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbd0cd6166fe5d82147280a6bad0f07285e6c81","tid":298084,"uid":124662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:10:35.000Z","msg":"80年代有梅豔芳, 90-00 年代有 Kelly, Sammi<br />\n好懷念果種熱血沸騰聽廣東話快歌既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n綜觀今時今日香港樂壇只係得返鍾舒漫一個跳唱女歌手<br />\n（可能仲有, 巴打請提醒）<br />\n<br />\n老實講 Sherman 跳舞真係唔差<br />\n最新果首快歌係funky style, 王雙駿幫佢做, 聽落幾型幾有feel<br />\n而家樂壇得佢一個唱依種歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8SgRP9BnmTA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8SgRP9BnmTA&d=QXPzg7KFaPO1RB7uCK5ohghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0d9a9c21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8SgRP9BnmTA</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔係佢忠粉<br />\n但係都欣賞佢仍然行跳唱路線<br />\n希望旦記唔好再逼佢唱情歌<br />\n跳多d舞 令香港樂壇唔好再咁單一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d52f094396d20b726372455211d03b6187b3726","tid":298084,"uid":2319,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:17:14.000Z","msg":"佢d快歌真係幾正<br />\n一出道隻高手過招 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有SC隻碟"},{"pid":"71e94f2988f798595ea7c35196f21bc966c40f01","tid":298084,"uid":124662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢d快歌真係幾正<br />\n一出道隻高手過招 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有SC隻碟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最緊要係而家香港冇人做依類音樂<br />\n我覺得要支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fd364d3acb0e3909fd7b7e49028f6ba3d38798","tid":298084,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"跳唱實